{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d663dd0e9d","title":"中共浙江省委办公厅关于全省公共食堂情况的材料","origin":"浙江省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9d21f2954d","index":0,"year":1959,"month":6,"day":12,"articleId":"d663dd0e9d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"32ac34aa9e","type":"title","text":"中共浙江省委办公厅关于全省公共食堂情况的材料","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"89ecd2f2ed","type":"paragraph","text":"此件印发给省委各常委、秘书长和省委农工部戴星明同志参考。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"e4b1fb1a9b","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共浙江省委办公厅1959年6月12日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"83529de8ff","type":"appellation","text":"总号  89  共印22分","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"6493adafe4","type":"subtitle","text":"全省公共食堂情况","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"17f93644b8","type":"paragraph","text":"据五月十一日各地汇报，全省现在食堂十万零四千三百七十七个，比权力下放前增加四千零一十二个。目前已查明垮台的食堂二千一百九十一个，占食堂总数的百分之二点一。其中温州地区垮台的七百五十九个，宁波地区半停半炊的有二百三十五个，完全停伙的有三百个。停停办办的情况比较普遍。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"fd2fca9bc2","type":"paragraph","text":"在现有的食堂中，一日三稀的占百分之三十七点八；二稀一干的占百分之二十八点七；二干一稀的占百分之二十九点六；春耕春种大忙期间，水稻高产地区，一日三干或二干二稀的有三千九百七十一个，占百分之三点九。昌化县现有的一千四百三十一个食堂，全部一日三稀。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"e3663bb79c","type":"paragraph","text":"附：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"9bf37a5dfb","type":"subtitle","text":"全省公共食堂情况统计表","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"d663dd0e9d"},{"id":"3b5add1576","type":"subtitle","text":"1959年5月11日电话汇报","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","arti